Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.15,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Do you need a receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.22,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.37,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Who should I address it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.12,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,British Secret Intelligence Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.06,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Yes... Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.09,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,You can use the initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:23.69,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Oh, don't write MI6, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.89,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Write SIS instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:29.63,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,You sure like to joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:33.08,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,That aside, you're quite the drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:41.18,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,I always get an urge to drink after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:50.19,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,That night club's a joke. How can they employ hosts that get drunk before a customer does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.20,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.67,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.26,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Pick up the phone, November.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:28.17,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Thank you for calling. This is your beloved Jack Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:31.25,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Sorry I can't come to the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.30,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Let me leave you with a joke instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:38.75,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The shepherd said to the minister, "My wife is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:43.32,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,This is April. I've found February, our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:02:00.12,Location,,0,0,0,,{\c&H202228&\fs44\fnArial}Kabuki Street {\fscx200}-{\fscx95} Best in town
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.37,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.82,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,She'll live. She hasn't regained consciousness yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:24.02,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Is the rumor about her appearance in Tokyo true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.31,DTB-Default,Navi,0,0,0,,You have one saved message.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:35.39,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,This is April. I've found February, our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.39,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,She's being accompanied by a Caucasian boy with heterochromatic eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.43,DTB-Default,Cabbie,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.52,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Follow the car ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:51.14,DTB-Default,Navi,0,0,0,,4:04 A.M. End of messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:03:01.54,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,I thought about making a visit here after attending a funeral for an old navy friend in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:10.13,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,February, huh? Who would have thought she'd appear right in front of us after she went missing for five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.66,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Who was accompanying her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:16.48,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The details, including the cause of the explosion, are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:22.45,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,There's a saying in this country that goes "there's no use crying over spilt milk".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:29.98,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about the fact that she was a double agent who stole gate-related information from us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.07,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,and gave it to that syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:40.39,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,We also can't do anything about the fact that Great Britain lost an advantage in contractor-related research because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:47.74,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about what was spilt, but we can punish the maid who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.56,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Why now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:56.39,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Do you think her appearance and the upcoming solar maximum are related in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.98,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:06.11,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Suspend all other duties and prioritize the apprehension of February.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.97,DTB-Default,Assistant,0,0,0,,Solar maximum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:22.93,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Once every few years, the largest sunspots, classified by their Zurich number, appear in clusters on the surface of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.55,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,It looks like a gigantic eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.95,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Eyeball? That sounds creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.93,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,This phenomenon wasn't observed before the emergence of the gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.40,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,so there's been a tense atmosphere around the observatory for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.44,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Is something going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:42.61,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Something might happen, but something might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:47.82,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,There hasn't been any recent activity considered to be related. To be honest, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.60,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,There's something that's been bothering me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:58.11,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Five years ago, during the last solar maximum, the gate in South America disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.86,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,"Please protect your smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.77,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.05,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,No, I must express gratitude in these kinds of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.98,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.27,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,and nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.72,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.46,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'm Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Was that a gift from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.20,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I received it from somebody important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.44,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I see. You should take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.97,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What was it doing in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.00,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.17,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Who would have thought District 45 would be targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.88,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:09.99,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,According to information from an informant in forensics, not even a sliver of the meteor fragment could be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:17.87,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.63,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Footprints of a MI6 agent were left on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:28.33,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The same agent we came into contact with during the Havoc mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.24,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why would MI6 do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.17,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There aren't any limits of restraint as far as PANDORA is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:42.61,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a melting pot of countries with their own priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:47.82,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if news about the stolen meteor fragment already reached the U.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:04.37,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,What were you thinking, returning to the scene of the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.14,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I lost something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:12.27,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,It landed in a tree during the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.04,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amagiri, I met an interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.18,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,He was nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.41,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,For some reason, it felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.50,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.59,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.86,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Were you being followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.06,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.84,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,We've obtained the meteor fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.81,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,We'll leave this town in a state of chaos and animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.06,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.25,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Where's Amber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.33,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.54,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,She left to look for the final key.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.66,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Final key?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.53,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.60,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.98,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:04.84,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Is she meeting with someone, by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.07,DTB-Default,Vendor,0,0,0,,That'll be 480 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(962,329)}Episode Fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(851,599)}Memories of Betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,649)}in an Amber Smile... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,710)}(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.82,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:49.77,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,just because the solar maximum is occurring doesn't mean the phenomenon that took place in South America will occur here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.81,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:55.03,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,or Tokyo would have disappeared several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:59.37,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,However, I do consider it to be one of the indicators for preliminary activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.64,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,If multiple, simultaneous occurrences are confirmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.65,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Are there any other indicators?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:15.26,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,For example, during the last solar maximum that led to the disappearance of the South American gate, Hoshimi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:22.07,DTB-Default,Assistant,0,0,0,,Chief Ishizaki! Chief Ishizaki! Please return to the observation room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:27.45,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,The stars are whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:31.18,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,The stars are whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:34.33,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Happily, sorrowfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:39.32,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Glittering, shimmering...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.89,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.73,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.66,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Hoshimi-sama spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.94,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,No way! Saitou-san, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.53,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Kanei Trade Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.66,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,where MI6's Tokyo branch is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.58,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The floor housing the British Intelligence Service was targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.91,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,It seems like they're growing restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.99,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Information about their initial course of action has been leaked all the way down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:17.16,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Apparently, there were traces of CIA involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.97,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.20,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Kirihara Misaki, Chief of Foreign Affairs, Division Four, at your...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.79,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Mr. Nishijima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.31,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Treat what I'm about to tell you as off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:40.44,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Three weeks ago, a certain prohibited material was smuggled from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:45.35,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,A CIA agent was believed to have been initially involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.70,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,but the people who smuggled it were from another organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.43,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.20,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,That's what the CIA is speculating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:12:02.40,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,The U.K. suddenly lost any advantage it once had regarding contractor-related research as a result of the information leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.47,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,They have been visibly apprehensive in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:11.56,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Did the CIA blow up the MI6 branch in order to retrieve the gate-proprietary material?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.12,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,That is only an assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:35.19,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,First MI6, and now the CIA building?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.75,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the English retaliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:43.43,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's not it. It looks like a different intelligence agency has been interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.60,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:50.83,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe all of them are trying to start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:55.73,Location,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6a7567&\fs20\fnArial}Shinjyuku Shaken!! Reoccurring explosions of buildings a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:56.17,DTB-Default,Caster,0,0,0,,Another explosion took place at the Pacific Central Tower, which occurred after the attack on the Kanei Trade Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.73,DTB-Default,Caster,0,0,0,,Many survivors are still trapped inside the tower, unable to escape due to the ensuing fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.99,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.06,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Who was responsible for it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:28.13,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,I'm still waiting for the report from an undercover agent conducting espionage on the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.75,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop by the American embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.72,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Continue with the search and apprehension of February.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:39.05,DTB-Default,Decade,0,0,0,,Forget about periodic updates. Call me when there's some kind of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.27,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.49,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.62,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:59.05,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The stolen meteor fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:02.86,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,"I don't know what you're talking about, ask somebody else" is what I should be telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.38,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,but that aside, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.24,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I also have something I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.74,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Where's February?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.83,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,My information says she's in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.14,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Her code name within your organization is Amber, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.46,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Amber is... in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.84,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I bet the Shinjuku explosion this morning was her work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.15,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,since it was confirmed by one of our agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:31.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Did the agent see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.03,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,She was a victim of the explosion and is in critical condition as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:38.02,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Tell me where she is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.45,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.67,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The fact that she's a member of your organization is more than...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.96,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.59,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Were you also deceived by her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.97,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,She's pretty bold for a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.72,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,A Lilith in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.46,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did Amber show up in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.73,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.34,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't lay a hand on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.17,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I'll take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.48,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:22.66,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,This is November. I need the latest information on the bombing of the CIA building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:29.21,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,According to the undercover agent, there were traces of activity from the Chinese Ministry of State Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.08,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The next target is the Chinese embassy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.43,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,They're leaving an easy trail to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.68,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Although we don't know their objectives, this works out in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.02,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,She's being accompanied by a Caucasian boy with heterochromatic eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.53,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Heterochromia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.21,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,If anything happens, be sure to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.09,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Where's February?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.18,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Code name Amber. Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.87,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.47,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I guess I don't have any other choice but to force you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:40.18,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,We have no need for him if he was defeated that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.56,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Use three recorders and get a backup ready, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.87,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Set the auxiliary organic media to recordable temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.60,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Don't cut off the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:59.49,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Oh, set up a connection with the Crisis Management Center in the Prime Minister's Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.13,DTB-Default,Assistant,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.49,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Ishizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:07.88,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,This is the second time I've heard Hoshimi-sama speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.25,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,The first time was during the solar maximum five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.12,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:18.42,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Yes, when part of South America disappeared from the world as we knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:25.29,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Shiny and bright, the stars are twinkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.72,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Strong and weak, they are singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:33.00,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,I can hear it, just like that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.71,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,It's almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.91,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,The beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.65,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,The beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.60,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I can't find the bread knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.37,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Can I use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.24,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I like the smell of freshly baked bread,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:04.64,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,spread with a generous serving of lime marmalade and topped with whipped cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.89,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Should we run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:12.31,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Somewhere... Somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.27,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You, Pai, and me, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.16,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,A place where we can see the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.32,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.69,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It's a good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:46.78,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,"Please protect your smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.67,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What? She appeared in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's Amber, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.16,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Maybe Yin knows where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.20,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.95,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It may sound strange coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:14.97,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.32\fnArial\bord0\shad0\fs60\frz20.272\pos(679,189)\c&H3E324F&}Tobacco
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.19,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,but I really like this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.71,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.41,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Yes. Nice to meet you, Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.29,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.11,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Amber...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:46.96,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The familiar name called out is silenced by a vengeful blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:51.97,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Trembling about a significant loss, crying over an irretrievable dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.45,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Revenge is the bread that sustains life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.75,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Sorrow is a poisonous spice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:02.16,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Envy, fear, and misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.26,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The unleashed trap is in the form of a human soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Sixteen Memories of Betrayal in an Amber Smile... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.69,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,and something is on the verge of change.